  "texts": [
    "Ensuring transparency in AI decision-making processes and regularly auditing AI systems for bias can further enhance fairness and build customer trust.",
    "AI systems in customer service depend on having an accurate and up-to-date knowledge base in order to work well.",
    "If the information is incomplete or outdated, it can lead to the AI providing incorrect responses and result in lower customer satisfaction.",
    "The quality of the AI's output is directly connected to the quality of the knowledge it has access to.",
    "To tackle this challenge, future directions involve improving the methods used to maintain and update knowledge bases."
  ],
